2>  <ul><li> Agnello 1950 62 no.20 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002213\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002213</a>  </li><li> Manganaro 1988 47 n.231 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001427\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001427</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> <p>Tall regular letters, deeply cut: Alpha with broken bar; omicron in rhomboid form; sigma lunate but square in form; kappa with short arms; epsilon standard with equal length horizontal bars; a large diamond shape interpunct in line 1</p> Line 1  50-60 (but omicron sigma 40-45)  Line 2  62-66  Interlineation line 1 to 2  not measured  </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
